<div class="com-share-favor" data-id="25" data-title="《嘘，DNA可以保密了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/25/medium/25.png?1436635433" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/articles/25.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
